label.phrase: the strategy we use for q2 is really to grow the active paying accounts and trying to convert more of the non-paying accounts into active accounts and on top of that we try to extend the life cycle of the games and trying not to grow output too much so in fact the launching of virtual items during q2 has been slowed down so that explains the decrease in the output i think that's a strategy that we adopt to extend the life cycle of the game
